General.Name: Agrieuro Corp
General.Description: AgriEuro Corp. engages in the agriculture, aquaculture, and hospitality businesses. It operates a reed farm covering an area of approximately 700 hectares; fish farm that consists of 1009 hectares; and building complex with a constructed surface of 1,200 square meters, as well as an island holiday complex. The company was founded in 2013 and is based in Bucharest, Romania. AgriEuro Corp. is a subsidiary of Speed Flyer Limited.
